{"word":"G5361 - φιλάδελφος - philádelphos - fil-ad'-el-fos - Love as brethren","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">φιλάδελφος</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">philádelphos</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">fil-ad'-el-fos</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Love as brethren</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Adjective / பெயரடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"சகோதர சிநேகமுள்ள - பெயரடை"},{"paragraph":"loving brother or sister"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G5384 - φίλος - phílos - fee'-los/5384\">G5384</a> and <a href=\"#/G80 - ἀδελφός - adelphós - ad-el-fos'/80\">G80</a>; <i>fond of brethren</i>, that is, <i>fraternal:</i> - love as brethren.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G5360/5360\">G5360</a>, <a href=\"#/G5361/5361\">G5361</a>, <a href=\"#/G5569/5569\">G5569</a>, <a href=\"#/G79/79\">G79</a>, <a href=\"#/G80/80\">G80</a>, <a href=\"#/G81/81\">G81</a>"}]}